29:37.826 --> 29:40.310
Do you want to join the church?

29:40.370 --> 29:41.652
Do you need a church family?

29:42.232 --> 29:43.554
Tell them I walk down with you.

29:44.195 --> 29:45.016
Only count of three.

29:45.217 --> 29:45.878
One, two, three.

29:45.998 --> 29:46.659
Ask somebody.

29:47.119 --> 29:48.421
Put a smile on your face.

29:49.863 --> 29:51.165
Fix your face, amen.

29:51.846 --> 29:53.408
Like my momma said, fix your face.

29:54.390 --> 29:55.351
Get your mind right.

29:59.738 --> 30:02.321
You got a smile when you talk about Jesus, amen.

30:04.044 --> 30:05.586
Don't be mean, bugging amen.

30:07.426 --> 30:10.630
Hey, man, y'all, y'all remember your momma used to tell you to fix your face now.

30:15.495 --> 30:19.500
Repeat after me, God, I thank you for the gift of salvation.

30:21.322 --> 30:22.524
God, I admit I'm a sinner.

30:24.586 --> 30:34.738
I believe that Jesus Christ died for me and was resurrected on the third day for the salvation of my sins.

30:36.514 --> 30:43.925
God, I confess Jesus Christ as Savior and Lord of my life.

30:45.287 --> 30:53.219
And I'm going to do what He tells me to do so I can be who He wants me to be.

30:54.741 --> 30:55.182
Amen.

30:55.923 --> 30:57.685
That's the first time you've prayed that prayer.

30:57.705 --> 30:58.827
I want you to walk forward.

30:59.328 --> 31:02.172
If you prayed that prayer, you comprehend it, you digest it.

31:02.693 --> 31:03.634
Please be seated.

31:06.562 --> 31:14.482
Watch the apple out deacons and associate ministers are coming forward now as we partake of the Lord's Supper and distribute the elements.

